sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as 用戶端 (Frontend)
    participant Filter as Security Filter (JwtAuthenticationFilter)
    participant AuthAPI as AuthController
    participant Service as AuthService
    participant DB as 資料庫 (User Table)
    participant Context as SecurityContext / Session

    Note over Client, Context: 【 階段一：登入驗證 (Login & Issue Tokens) 】
    Client->>AuthAPI: POST /api/auth/login (email, password)
    AuthAPI->>Service: authenticate() & createAuthResponse()
    Service->>DB: 查詢用戶 & 驗證密碼 (BCrypt)
    Service->>DB: 產生並儲存 UUID (RT-1) 效期 7 天
    Service-->>AuthAPI: 回傳 { accessToken: JWT(AT-1), refreshToken: RT-1 }
    AuthAPI-->>Client: 200 OK (前端儲存雙 Token & Set-Cookie 標頭將 JSESSIONID 傳回給瀏覽器)

    Note over Client, Context: 【 階段二：一般授權操作 (JWT Validation) 】
    Client->>Filter: 呼叫 API (Header: Bearer AT-1)
    Filter->>Filter: 解析並校驗 JWT (Signature & Expiration)
    Filter->>Context: 設定 Authentication (email, authorities)
    Context-->>AuthAPI: 通過過濾器抵達 Controller
    AuthAPI-->>Client: 200 OK (正常回應業務數據)

    Note over Client, Context: 【 階段三：權杖輪換 (Refresh Token Rotation) 】
    Client->>Filter: 呼叫 API (AT-1 已過期)
    Filter-->>Client: 401 Unauthorized (Access Token Expired)

    Client->>AuthAPI: POST /api/auth/refresh (Body: { refreshToken: RT-1 })
    AuthAPI->>Service: refreshToken(RT-1)
    Service->>DB: 驗證 RT-1 是否存在且未過期
    DB-->>Service: 驗證通過

    rect rgb(235, 245, 255)
        Note right of Service: [安全性核心] 舊 RT-1 立即作廢並核發新 RT
        Service->>DB: 產生全新 UUID (RT-2) 覆蓋 RT-1
    end

    Service-->>AuthAPI: 回傳 { 新 AT-2, 新 RT-2 }
    AuthAPI-->>Client: 200 OK (前端必須更新 AT-2, RT-2)

    Note over Client, Context: 【 階段四：安全性登出 (Logout & Revocation) 】
    Client->>AuthAPI: POST /api/auth/logout (Bearer AT-2)

    rect rgb(255, 240, 240)
        Note right of AuthAPI: [徹底清除] Session 與 Refresh Token 狀態
        AuthAPI->>Context: session.invalidate()
        AuthAPI->>Service: logout()
        Service->>DB: 將該使用者的 refreshToken 欄位設為 NULL
        Service->>Context: SecurityContextHolder.clearContext()
    end

    AuthAPI-->>Client: 200 OK (Logout successful)
    Note over Client: 前端主動刪除本機存儲的<br/>所有 Access & Refresh Tokens
